# 🚗 Car Auction Telegram Bot

A Telegram bot built with **Aiogram** for managing online car auctions.  
Users can register, browse available cars, place bids, and track auction status — all directly within Telegram.

---

## 📦 Features

- User registration and authentication  
- Create and manage car auctions  
- Real-time bidding via inline buttons  
- Admin panel for managing users and listings  
- PostgreSQL database with Alembic migrations  

---

## ⚙️ Deployment

### 1. Environment setup

sudo nano .env
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m app.bot.init
2. Database migrations
Generate a new migration:


alembic revision --autogenerate -m "name"
Apply migrations:


alembic upgrade head
🗂 Project Structure
app/db → database logic (models, CRUD, migrations)

app/bot/routers → Telegram update handlers and bot logic

app/bot/init → bot startup and dispatcher setup

🛠 Tech Stack
Python 3.10+

Aiogram (Telegram bot framework)

PostgreSQL

Alembic (for migrations)

Docker (optional for deployment)

🚀 Usage
Configure .env with your database URL and Telegram bot token

Run migrations to prepare the database

Start the bot:

bash
python -m 
